code: import axios from"axios";export const processAudio=async(formData,setUploadProgress)=>{const response=await axios.post("http://54.252.148.37/process-audio",formData,{headers:{"Content-Type":"multipart/form-data"},onUploadProgress:progressEvent=>{const percentCompleted=Math.round(progressEvent.loaded*100/progressEvent.total);setUploadProgress(percentCompleted);}});return response.data;};
